			<div>
				<h1
					class="text-white text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold flex flex-row gap-x-4 pb-6 lg:pb-10"
				>
					Hey, I'm Samuele <a
						href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/samuele-spinetti"
						target="_blank"
						rel="noopener"
						class="flex justify-center items-center"
					>
						<Badge>Open to work</Badge>
					</a>
				</h1>
				<h2
					class="text-xl lg:text-2xl opacity-80 text-wrap max-w-[700px]"
				>
					<span class="text-yellow-200/90"
						>Full Stack Web Developer.</span
					>
					<span class="text-red-200/90"
						>Italian based in Barcelona, Spain ðŸ‡®ðŸ‡¹ðŸ‡ªðŸ‡¸â€‹
					</span>
